img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n腸道必須徹底清理，準備妥當，才能讓大腸鏡醫生清楚檢視你的腸道。腸道不徹底清理，會留下糞便妨礙檢查，影響檢查結果。<br />\n因果關係都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢可能唔知要飲瀉藥先照到腸鏡<br />\n柯到最後d屎真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前照前柯唔清俾醫生叫灌腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931a6a9c847de55e9c2f72a4b40001fc205a6ed2","tid":193464,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/9joqmb.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhealth%2F9joqmb.html&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0c0a5b57\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/9joqmb.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e0530182e7a93e4990656038d746bee716101a","tid":193464,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/9joqmb.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhealth%2F9joqmb.html&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0c0a5b57\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/9joqmb.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc